Definition: a word specifying identity or spatial or temporal location from the perspective of a speaker or hearer in the context in which the communication occurs
Example: words that introduce particulars of the speaker's and hearer's shared cognitive field into the message- R.Rommetveit
Synonyms: adj, pert, deictic_word, word, a, specifying, identity, or, spatial, temporal, location, from, the, perspective, of, speaker, hearer, in, context, which, communication, occurs, words, that, introduce, particulars, s, and, shared, cognitive, field, into, message, -, R, Rommetveit
Category: noun.communication
